Ultrasonic Sensor
      VCC   -->   5V (NodeMCU)
      GND   -->   GND (NodeMCU)
      Trig  -->   D1 (NodeMCU)
      Echo  -->   D2 (NodeMCU)

NodeMCU (ESP8266)
      VCC   -->   5V (Power Supply)
      GND   -->   GND (Power Supply)
      D1    -->   Trig Pin (Ultrasonic Sensor)
      D2    -->   Echo Pin (Ultrasonic Sensor)

